  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (Minimal profile)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions at Model Risk Level 5. The intended use is prediction of absolute hemolysis index values to support a Class III VAD 510(k) submission. All thirteen credibility factors have been evaluated; seven achieved their required gradation levels and six were scoped out as not applicable for this operating regime. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification was performed across all uncertain model inputs. Based on the totality of evidence and the Low assurance level assigned to this submission, the credibility assessment team accepted the model for the stated VAD use scope.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/vad-hemolysis-mrl5-req-001",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/vad-hemolysis-cfd-claim-001",
  "bindsModel": "https://uofa.net/synth/model/fda-generic-centrifugal-pump-cfd-v3",
  "bindsDataset": [
    "https://uofa.net/synth/data/fda-pump-piv-experimental-dataset",
    "https://uofa.net/synth/data/fda-pump-hemolysis-benchmark-dataset"
  ],
